rows.label: tlk41300021_04_msg0001
rows.name:
All I hear from the adventurers
and merchants who come to
this port is anxiety.

rows.label: tlk41300021_04_msg0002
rows.name:
The great Divine Beast Acedia has sunk,
and three other powerful Divine Beasts
have gathered at the World Tree...

rows.label: tlk41300021_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Fortunately, Gula is still far from the World
Tree... But people who think Gula is safe will
probably start flooding in from now on.

rows.label: tlk41300021_04_msg0005
rows.name:
At what point did things
get like this...?

rows.label: tlk41300021_04_msg0006
rows.name:
The world has become a place far
removed from the word "peace"...
